fix: three root issues. (1) Session persistence: _extract_session_id was returning None — the ResultMessage.session_id field exists but was never read. Now captures it from every ResultMessage (not just first), handles session_id changes after compaction. This was the root cause of 'session=new' on every call, which broke sub-agent context and conversation continuity. (2) Logs tab: new LogsTab.svelte in agent profile, polls container logs every 5s. Added agents.logs() API method. (3) Activity logging: ActivityManager.log() now called in processor.rs record_and_store (agent_response events) and dispatcher.rs poll_once (task_completed events). Dashboard recent activity is now clickable, linking to agent logs tab, color-coded by event type.
